# Overage commit template — single-line subject only.
# Format: <type>(scope?): <lowercase imperative subject>
# Types:  feat fix docs refactor test ci chore perf style build
# Rules:  all lowercase, no period at end, <= 72 chars, single line, no body, no trailers.
#         (PR_TITLE becomes the squash subject on main; BLANK strips bodies/trailers.)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add anthropic provider adapter
#   fix(proxy): handle missing reasoning_tokens
#   ci: enforce conventional commits via commit-lint workflow
#
# Forbidden: Signed-off-by:, Co-authored-by:, Made-with:, Generated-by:.
#
# Activate this template once per clone:
#   git config commit.template .gitmessage
